WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 35]

02:51.000 --> 02:52.850
If I really want something,

02:52.900 --> 02:54.030
I don't trade for it.

02:54.800 --> 02:55.780
I just

02:56.000 --> 02:56.690
take it.

02:57.410 --> 02:59.220
Since you know what I did

02:59.250 --> 03:00.350
was a trick,

03:00.380 --> 03:01.820
why aren't you leaving?

03:01.840 --> 03:03.190
Didn't you say

03:03.230 --> 03:04.620
I'm arrogant

03:04.650 --> 03:05.720
and that the harder something is,

03:05.740 --> 03:06.990
the more I want to do it?

03:07.220 --> 03:08.500
Then

03:08.530 --> 03:09.440
I suddenly don't want to leave.

03:10.590 --> 03:13.160
So, you still want to destroy the Xing Yue Bow?

03:13.180 --> 03:15.860
Then I can't let you stay in the Lunar Race's territory.

03:18.310 --> 03:20.370
I've decided not to use any tricks to defeat you.

03:20.650 --> 03:22.620
I'm going to have a fair fight with you.

03:22.850 --> 03:24.160
If you win,

03:24.180 --> 03:25.490
I will never think

03:25.520 --> 03:27.210
about destroying the Xing Yue Divine Bow again.

03:27.570 --> 03:28.590
Besides, the Demon Race

03:28.640 --> 03:30.790
will never fight against the Lunar Race again.

03:31.100 --> 03:32.100
Of course,

03:32.130 --> 03:33.860
you can't use the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

03:33.880 --> 03:35.510
Otherwise, it'll be too unfair.

03:36.550 --> 03:38.410
Why should I agree to that?

03:40.250 --> 03:41.740
I saved you last night.

03:42.400 --> 03:44.850
I don't think you want to owe me a favor.

03:47.210 --> 03:48.160
When shall we fight?

03:50.829 --> 03:52.579
I'm still staying in that small room.

03:52.610 --> 03:55.070
When the Hidden power inside your body is gone,

03:55.120 --> 03:56.720
it will be the day of our battle.

03:58.250 --> 03:59.070
Okay.

04:01.400 --> 04:03.140
You haven't promised me.

04:03.160 --> 04:03.910
If you lose...

04:03.910 --> 04:04.690
There's no need.

04:04.720 --> 04:06.250
I won't lose.

04:11.900 --> 04:12.860
My Lord,

04:12.890 --> 04:14.760
are you really letting the Demon Lord stay in our territory?

04:18.190 --> 04:20.700
He's here to destroy the Xing Yue Divine Bow!

04:20.990 --> 04:22.900
Since I promised him,

04:22.920 --> 04:24.520
I should have a fair fight with him.

04:24.550 --> 04:25.340
My Lord,

04:25.360 --> 04:27.360
don't be tricked by him.

04:27.390 --> 04:28.560
Across the three parts of the Divine Region,

04:28.580 --> 04:30.380
the Demon Lord is famous for being impetuous and conceited.

04:30.410 --> 04:31.840
He never cares about any divine rules.

04:31.920 --> 04:34.159
He's no different from the Hidden Lord.

04:34.190 --> 04:35.310
Besides,

04:35.330 --> 04:36.320
if the elders know

04:36.360 --> 04:37.690
you let the Demon Lord stay here...

04:39.580 --> 04:40.530
Xiu Yan,

04:41.110 --> 04:42.480
what are you worried about?

04:42.750 --> 04:43.750
My Lord.

04:44.540 --> 04:46.220
The Contemplation Stone's Divine Contemplations are unstable.

04:47.040 --> 04:48.240
Your mind...

04:49.870 --> 04:50.890
is wavering.

04:55.210 --> 04:56.510
Don't worry.

04:56.600 --> 04:58.550
I know what I'm doing.

04:58.580 --> 05:00.040
-My Lord...
-You may leave.

05:33.110 --> 05:35.800
I can't believe you're feeding the Soul Lotus with your blood.

05:36.090 --> 05:37.290
Shut up.

05:37.800 --> 05:39.090
It's none of your business.

05:39.870 --> 05:41.280
How exactly do you feel

05:41.300 --> 05:42.990
about the Lunar Lord?

05:43.360 --> 05:45.230
That's not something you should ask.

06:05.480 --> 06:09.230
♫The person standing far away♫

06:09.830 --> 06:12.160
♫Don't be afraid♫

06:12.540 --> 06:17.130
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

06:18.100 --> 06:24.490
♫Walk towards me♫

06:26.140 --> 06:29.000
♫My heart feels so...♫

06:29.610 --> 06:35.590
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

06:37.450 --> 06:41.220
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

06:44.930 --> 06:48.190
♫You are my distant call♫

06:48.760 --> 06:53.130
♫You are my first and last♫

06:53.960 --> 06:59.870
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

07:00.280 --> 07:03.160
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

07:04.120 --> 07:07.750
♫Let's never let go♫

07:13.000 --> 07:14.790
The weather is clear today.

07:14.810 --> 07:16.400
Playing go has made you happy.

07:16.430 --> 07:17.660
Why don't you fight now?

07:17.940 --> 07:19.890
I just lost the game.

07:19.910 --> 07:21.250
What makes you think

07:21.270 --> 07:22.600
I'm happy?

07:27.720 --> 07:32.180
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

07:32.460 --> 07:34.909
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

07:35.610 --> 07:39.110
♫The one who was slightly late♫

07:37.940 --> 07:40.010
You finally fought! Who won?

07:39.900 --> 07:47.170
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

07:40.040 --> 07:40.680
Who won?

07:40.700 --> 07:42.380
Why are you so excited?

07:42.409 --> 07:43.530
Our fingers got itchy today.

07:43.550 --> 07:44.720
We were just trying swordsmanship

07:44.750 --> 07:46.140
to prepare for the future battle.

07:48.550 --> 07:55.400
♫You enriched my life♫

07:55.800 --> 08:00.770
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

08:03.320 --> 08:07.070
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

08:07.780 --> 08:12.320
♫You are my determined way home♫

08:12.830 --> 08:18.140
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

08:19.070 --> 08:22.750
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

08:23.030 --> 08:25.520
♫Let's never let go♫

09:17.650 --> 09:19.970
How long did that last?

09:20.130 --> 09:20.980
100 years.

09:22.390 --> 09:23.580
100 years?

09:24.000 --> 09:25.470
100 years wasn't enough

09:25.550 --> 09:26.870
to remove the Hidden power inside Xing Yue's body?

09:27.180 --> 09:29.410
What was hard to remove was not the Hidden power

09:29.440 --> 09:31.000
but love.

09:31.060 --> 09:32.790
The Demon Lord watered the Soul Lotus

09:32.810 --> 09:34.610
with his blood every night

09:34.980 --> 09:37.550
to help it produce spiritual energy more quickly.

09:37.760 --> 09:39.670
The Hidden power inside the Lunar Lord's body

09:39.730 --> 09:41.940
had been removed in the 10th year.

09:41.960 --> 09:43.630
In the next 90 years,

09:43.660 --> 09:45.380
day after day,

09:45.800 --> 09:48.710
they never fulfilled their promise to fight.

09:49.000 --> 09:50.240
I know

09:50.690 --> 09:52.210
it's not that they couldn't.

09:53.240 --> 09:54.550
They just didn't want to.

09:55.300 --> 09:56.750
One was a Lunar,

09:56.780 --> 09:58.460
the other a demon.

09:58.580 --> 10:00.060
They were on different sides, after all.

10:01.200 --> 10:02.580
That promise

10:03.240 --> 10:05.280
might be their only excuse

10:05.320 --> 10:06.470
to stay together for 100 years.

10:06.490 --> 10:07.920
For humans,

10:08.470 --> 10:10.280
100 years is a long time.

10:10.330 --> 10:12.000
It may be the length of their whole life.

10:12.610 --> 10:14.190
But for deities,

10:14.450 --> 10:16.500
100 years is just a moment.

10:16.740 --> 10:18.970
Before they noticed it,

10:19.590 --> 10:22.310
they were already deeply in love

10:22.390 --> 10:23.630
with each other.

10:24.330 --> 10:25.850
In that case,

10:25.880 --> 10:28.240
why didn't they just be together?

10:28.260 --> 10:29.450
Wasn't partnering up

10:29.480 --> 10:31.720
also a way to protect the world?

10:31.960 --> 10:32.920
Because

10:34.840 --> 10:36.350
Heaven didn't allow it.

10:44.830 --> 10:47.440
The Soul Lotus seems to have gained spiritual consciousness.

10:47.900 --> 10:49.540
It's inherently

10:49.560 --> 10:50.940
spiritual.

10:51.330 --> 10:53.370
After basking in the stellar power for 100 years,

10:53.390 --> 10:54.630
it's not surprising

10:54.660 --> 10:55.890
that it has gained spiritual consciousness.

10:56.210 --> 10:57.440
It's been 100 years.

10:59.040 --> 11:01.110
You've stayed in the Lunar Race's territory for 100 years.

11:01.130 --> 11:03.180
Have the elders from your race urged you to go back?

11:03.210 --> 11:05.390
They sent me letters every day to ask about my return date.

11:05.570 --> 11:07.210
I think it's time for me to go back.

11:09.470 --> 11:11.710
Are you going to go back first

11:12.060 --> 11:13.700
or fulfill the promise of a fight first?

11:13.730 --> 11:15.140
The promise of a fight?

11:19.230 --> 11:21.500
Do you think it's still necessary for us to fight?

11:33.180 --> 11:34.960
The tides of the Lunar Hidden Sea have ebbed and flowed for tens of thousands of years,

11:35.090 --> 11:36.300
creating some crystals.

11:37.070 --> 11:38.870
I found them interesting and collected them.

11:39.360 --> 11:41.050
You don't like jewelry,

11:41.080 --> 11:42.480
but this is made of stone.

11:42.500 --> 11:44.110
You're not going to refuse it, are you?

11:53.080 --> 11:54.970
Since you are about to leave,

11:55.320 --> 11:56.560
why are you suddenly

11:56.590 --> 11:57.560
giving me a gift?

11:57.580 --> 11:59.250
If you want to know why,

11:59.280 --> 12:01.370
go somewhere with me.

12:21.860 --> 12:23.050
The Purple Moon.

12:24.690 --> 12:25.600
The Demon Race?

12:27.180 --> 12:28.650
You've never been to our territory, have you?

12:30.560 --> 12:32.470
I've lived in your territory for 100 years.

12:32.500 --> 12:33.670
In return,

12:33.690 --> 12:36.050
don't you want to see the place I rule?

12:38.760 --> 12:42.510
♫Writing wishes in the night sky♫

12:40.690 --> 12:41.960
This is indeed

12:41.960 --> 12:43.720
my first time stepping on the Demon Race's territory.

12:43.220 --> 12:46.960
♫The clouds seal their approval for me♫

12:45.540 --> 12:47.470
It seems you demons

12:47.600 --> 12:50.280
neither have a strong demon aura nor fight endlessly

12:47.790 --> 12:51.540
♫You walk towards me slowly♫

12:50.760 --> 12:52.010
as rumor has it.

12:52.540 --> 12:55.250
♫Time stops♫

12:53.120 --> 12:55.330
Instead, you live a peaceful and stable life.

12:55.420 --> 12:57.980
And you're more free-spirited

12:56.720 --> 13:00.490
♫The brightest star in the night sky♫

12:59.420 --> 13:01.540
than I thought.

13:01.050 --> 13:05.050
♫Is willing to extinguish for you♫

13:02.170 --> 13:03.670
Free-spirited?

13:05.650 --> 13:09.840
♫Because the starlight in your eyes♫

13:07.130 --> 13:08.300
Actually, you can be free-spirited, too.

13:10.190 --> 13:13.750
♫Lights up my long night♫

13:17.080 --> 13:20.740
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

13:21.130 --> 13:24.960
♫Love you at every moment♫

13:26.020 --> 13:27.590
They are deities, too.

13:26.140 --> 13:28.060
♫Don't miss me♫

13:27.740 --> 13:29.800
They can change everything in the world

13:28.370 --> 13:33.010
♫I'll always be by your side♫

13:29.830 --> 13:31.030
and do whatever they want.

13:31.050 --> 13:32.720
Why are they still praying?

13:32.750 --> 13:34.360
Who are they praying to?

13:34.400 --> 13:36.960
The Purple Moon is the source of my divine power.

13:34.860 --> 13:38.010
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

13:36.980 --> 13:38.580
I can hear every wish

13:38.610 --> 13:39.970
made under the Purple Moon.

13:39.480 --> 13:42.840
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

13:39.990 --> 13:41.430
When I'm not busy,

13:41.550 --> 13:44.150
I'm willing to grant their wishes.

13:44.360 --> 13:46.490
♫Every starlight♫

13:44.610 --> 13:46.250
The source of divine power

13:46.280 --> 13:49.000
relates to the source of the power of the Three Races' Supreme Deities.

13:47.340 --> 13:51.430
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

13:49.200 --> 13:50.680
Why did you tell me that?

13:51.020 --> 13:52.930
Probably because

13:53.650 --> 13:54.930
I wanted to tell you.

13:59.750 --> 14:01.870
Just now, you asked how to live.

14:02.600 --> 14:04.020
But what they're asking for

14:04.280 --> 14:05.630
is love.

14:07.150 --> 14:08.680
Love?

14:08.940 --> 14:10.400
Love from their parents,

14:10.430 --> 14:12.080
friends,

14:11.790 --> 14:14.650
♫Writing wishes in the night sky♫

14:12.100 --> 14:13.530
teachers,

14:13.870 --> 14:15.460
and partners.

14:15.750 --> 14:19.240
♫The clouds seal their approval for me♫

14:15.860 --> 14:18.470
All they want

14:18.570 --> 14:19.890
is love.

14:20.300 --> 14:23.580
♫You walk towards me slowly♫

14:22.270 --> 14:23.480
So, Xing Yue,

14:23.500 --> 14:26.430
is there anything you want?

14:24.600 --> 14:27.540
♫Time stops♫

14:28.850 --> 14:33.160
♫The brightest star in the night sky♫

14:33.780 --> 14:37.700
♫Is willing to extinguish for you♫

14:37.400 --> 14:38.450
What about you?

14:38.230 --> 14:42.160
♫Because the starlight in your eyes♫

14:42.530 --> 14:46.570
♫Lights up my long night♫

14:49.360 --> 14:53.270
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

14:53.590 --> 14:57.140
♫Love you at every moment♫

14:54.400 --> 14:56.320
Why did you take me here?

14:56.900 --> 14:58.210
To answer your question

14:58.230 --> 14:59.690
at your place.

14:58.390 --> 15:00.320
♫Don't miss me♫

15:00.350 --> 15:01.210
Xing Yue,

15:00.760 --> 15:06.610
♫I'll always be by your side♫

15:02.020 --> 15:03.060
there's something I want.

15:05.130 --> 15:06.960
I was born as the Demon Lord.

15:07.140 --> 15:10.850
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

15:07.330 --> 15:08.900
For tens of thousands of years,

15:09.230 --> 15:11.410
I've been wanting to unite the Three Races

15:11.470 --> 15:12.860
and rule the Divine Region,

15:11.580 --> 15:16.150
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

15:13.330 --> 15:15.440
making everywhere my Purple Moon shines

15:15.830 --> 15:18.030
submit to the Demon Race.

15:16.790 --> 15:18.390
♫Every starlight♫

15:18.970 --> 15:23.050
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

15:23.130 --> 15:25.130
But that's what the Demon Lord wants,

15:25.310 --> 15:28.280
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

15:25.960 --> 15:27.190
not what Jing Yuan wants.

15:29.700 --> 15:32.490
♫I can't reach your world♫

15:29.860 --> 15:32.390
I only wish to stay with the one I love

15:32.990 --> 15:35.320
and take her to see the vast Divine Region

15:34.220 --> 15:36.370
♫The starlight in the sky♫

15:35.560 --> 15:36.900
and beautiful mountains and rivers

15:36.660 --> 15:42.070
♫Are all our souvenirs♫

15:37.280 --> 15:39.390
instead of just staying in the Xing Yue Pavilion.

15:39.620 --> 15:42.040
I want to enjoy the scenery of every race with her,

15:42.630 --> 15:44.470
experiencing all kinds of emotions and desires

15:43.540 --> 15:47.830
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

15:44.910 --> 15:47.310
and watching every sunrise and sunset.

15:48.160 --> 15:51.720
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

15:52.900 --> 15:54.860
♫Every starlight♫

15:55.200 --> 15:59.050
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

15:55.820 --> 15:56.890
Xing Yue.

15:57.940 --> 15:59.980
I want to be with you forever.

16:01.910 --> 16:03.790
Will you be my partner?

16:32.690 --> 16:33.980
I see.

16:41.660 --> 16:42.900
No, you don't.

16:47.680 --> 16:52.540
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

16:55.180 --> 16:58.330
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

16:59.550 --> 17:04.170
♫You are my determined way home♫

17:04.599 --> 17:10.260
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

17:10.720 --> 17:14.280
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

17:14.839 --> 17:16.869
♫Let's never let go♫

17:17.680 --> 17:22.200
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

17:24.670 --> 17:28.450
♫You are the blueprint of my life♫

17:52.330 --> 17:53.460
Why is this happening?

17:53.480 --> 17:55.150
The Lunar Lord didn't summon the Divine Bow.

18:16.870 --> 18:18.320
It's heading towards the Lunar Hidden Sea.

18:45.980 --> 18:47.020
Xing Yue,

18:47.050 --> 18:48.510
come with me to the Demon Race's territory

18:49.090 --> 18:50.780
and hold our wedding there.

18:51.950 --> 18:52.780
Okay?

18:58.440 --> 18:59.250
I...

19:23.380 --> 19:26.660
♫Across thousands of miles♫

19:25.600 --> 19:26.580
Jing Yuan!

19:31.760 --> 19:36.450
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

19:34.220 --> 19:35.290
Jing Yuan.

19:35.530 --> 19:36.770
Jing Yuan!

19:44.960 --> 19:46.020
Why?

19:46.330 --> 19:47.850
Why did you kill him?

19:49.000 --> 19:49.910
Because of you.

19:50.970 --> 19:52.080
Xing Yue,

19:52.100 --> 19:54.920
you were formed from the Heavenly stellar power.

19:55.270 --> 19:56.920
Maintaining peace in the Divine Region

19:56.950 --> 19:58.880
is the meaning of your existence.

19:59.100 --> 20:00.750
And my mission

20:00.780 --> 20:03.410
is to kill anyone who can make you waver.

20:03.450 --> 20:05.600
He had to die

20:05.700 --> 20:07.320
just because I fell in love with him?

20:08.160 --> 20:10.250
I couldn't control my feelings!

20:10.270 --> 20:11.620
I'm the one who fell in love!

20:11.650 --> 20:13.340
I'm the one who lost control of the Xing Yue Bow

20:13.360 --> 20:15.560
and broke the Heavenly rules!

20:15.590 --> 20:16.540
What did he do wrong?

20:16.590 --> 20:18.040
Why did he have to die?

20:18.240 --> 20:19.190
This

20:19.210 --> 20:21.070
is Heaven's will.

20:23.590 --> 20:27.560
♫The flowers flew away♫

20:31.060 --> 20:35.010
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

20:39.980 --> 20:47.120
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

20:42.460 --> 20:44.900
I was formed from the Heavenly power.

20:46.230 --> 20:47.750
My existence

20:47.920 --> 20:53.410
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

20:48.180 --> 20:50.000
sets the rules of the Divine Region.

20:50.600 --> 20:52.320
Heaven wanted him dead,

20:53.910 --> 20:55.670
but I want him to live.

21:05.540 --> 21:10.990
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

21:11.800 --> 21:13.070
My Lord, no!

21:13.620 --> 21:19.060
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

21:20.980 --> 21:28.360
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

21:28.970 --> 21:33.640
♫I'm your wanderer♫

21:37.290 --> 21:41.410
♫The flowers flew away♫

21:41.050 --> 21:43.250
My Lord, no!

21:43.270 --> 21:44.460
No!

21:45.000 --> 21:48.900
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

21:53.970 --> 22:00.920
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

22:01.130 --> 22:02.180
My Lord!

22:01.920 --> 22:07.400
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

22:02.910 --> 22:04.020
My Lord!

22:10.610 --> 22:12.220
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

22:12.580 --> 22:14.810
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

22:14.870 --> 22:16.660
♫My love brought tears♫

22:16.910 --> 22:18.630
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

22:18.720 --> 22:19.530
My Lord!

22:19.050 --> 22:20.880
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

22:20.070 --> 22:20.960
My Lord!

22:21.080 --> 22:22.290
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

22:22.550 --> 22:24.320
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

22:24.700 --> 22:26.420
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

22:26.900 --> 22:28.390
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

22:28.770 --> 22:30.420
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

22:30.800 --> 22:32.760
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

22:33.200 --> 22:34.710
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

22:35.150 --> 22:36.680
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

22:37.080 --> 22:39.090
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

22:39.480 --> 22:40.980
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

22:41.180 --> 22:43.640
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

22:45.360 --> 22:46.160
My Lord!

22:47.530 --> 22:48.460
My Lord,

22:48.490 --> 22:50.630
even though you made a divine pact with the Demon Lord

22:50.650 --> 22:52.000
to help him gather his divine soul

22:52.070 --> 22:53.310
and transfer the divine punishment from the Xing Yue Divine Bow

22:53.310 --> 22:55.000
to yourself,

22:55.030 --> 22:57.510
you can't make his feelings for you disappear.

22:57.650 --> 22:59.560
As long as he is by your side,

22:59.590 --> 23:01.250
and you two still love each other,

23:01.280 --> 23:02.440
the divine punishment from the Xing Yue Divine Bow

23:02.440 --> 23:04.160
will come again.

23:07.600 --> 23:10.090
Then I'll destroy his love

23:11.420 --> 23:13.870
for Xing Yue.

23:30.370 --> 23:32.030
His divine power is too strong.

23:32.430 --> 23:34.810
I could only seal his memory of tonight.

23:35.070 --> 23:36.510
When he wakes up,

23:36.540 --> 23:39.170
he won't remember the appearance of the Xing Yue Divine Arrow.

23:40.210 --> 23:41.410
Xiu Yan,

23:41.740 --> 23:43.170
never let him know

23:43.880 --> 23:46.080
what happened tonight.

23:46.850 --> 23:48.120
My Lord...

23:52.770 --> 23:54.180
After tonight,

23:54.640 --> 23:56.520
Xing Yue will become

23:56.850 --> 23:58.320
the person

23:59.670 --> 24:01.020
the Demon Lord hates the most.

24:06.330 --> 24:08.180
The Lunar Lord restored everything

24:08.910 --> 24:11.390
and pretended nothing had happened.

24:12.490 --> 24:15.460
Jing Yuan had no memory of being hurt by the Divine Bow.

24:16.290 --> 24:18.310
He followed his heart

24:19.020 --> 24:21.090
and confessed his love to the Lunar Lord again.

24:21.810 --> 24:23.010
That night,

24:23.540 --> 24:25.610
it snowed at the Lunar Hidden Sea for the first time

24:30.840 --> 24:33.050
in tens of thousands of years.

24:41.940 --> 24:44.520
I heard it hasn't snowed here for tens of thousands of years.

24:45.550 --> 24:47.380
We happen to see the first snow today.

24:48.240 --> 24:49.730
As we see the first snow together, we can grow old together.

24:50.170 --> 24:51.300
Perfect.

24:52.370 --> 24:53.370
Xing Yue.

24:55.340 --> 24:57.300
I want to be with you forever.

24:58.310 --> 25:00.310
Will you be my partner?

25:04.750 --> 25:06.470
Don't you think

25:07.250 --> 25:09.150
that's a ridiculous question?

25:11.820 --> 25:13.560
A deity's life is long.

25:13.940 --> 25:16.200
I let you stay in Xing Yue Pavilion

25:16.510 --> 25:18.590
because it's boring.

25:25.750 --> 25:27.100
I don't believe that.

25:28.010 --> 25:29.810
We were together for 100 years

25:29.980 --> 25:31.560
just because you were

25:31.990 --> 25:33.190
bored?

25:33.470 --> 25:35.050
Indeed, that's not all.

25:35.800 --> 25:37.520
I don’t like killing.

25:37.540 --> 25:39.940
So I am willing to spend 100 years

25:40.160 --> 25:42.160
to talk to the you

25:42.320 --> 25:43.880
and become friends.

25:43.900 --> 25:46.550
If you're willing to surrender

25:46.580 --> 25:48.610
and protect peace in the Divine Region,

25:48.630 --> 25:50.570
we can be

25:50.590 --> 25:52.120
friends.

25:52.890 --> 25:54.540
But what you want

25:54.860 --> 25:56.750
is too much.

25:58.330 --> 25:59.130
Too...

26:00.730 --> 26:01.690
Too much.

26:03.500 --> 26:05.870
I'm the Lunar Supreme Deity.

26:06.050 --> 26:07.850
I rule the stars

26:07.880 --> 26:09.560
and am as important as the heavens.

26:09.810 --> 26:11.530
In my eyes,

26:11.560 --> 26:12.760
everyone is

26:12.800 --> 26:14.030
the same to me.

26:14.310 --> 26:16.180
For peace in the Divine Region,

26:16.210 --> 26:18.060
I can make friends

26:18.080 --> 26:19.290
with you.

26:19.390 --> 26:21.540
But if you want me to lower myself to marry you,

26:22.460 --> 26:23.330
Demon Lord,

26:24.110 --> 26:25.460
you're crossing the line.

26:27.930 --> 26:29.580
There are so many beings...

26:30.610 --> 26:32.290
There is no difference...

26:36.370 --> 26:37.740
For the peace of the Divine Region,

26:38.370 --> 26:40.540
you can be my friend?

26:41.230 --> 26:42.270
Xing Yue.

26:42.700 --> 26:45.590
We've spent 100 years together, feeling the same for each other.

26:46.130 --> 26:48.500
Was it just to keep me in Lunar Race?

26:50.770 --> 26:51.770
Yes.

26:55.920 --> 26:57.530
What if I refuse to believe it?

27:04.070 --> 27:05.880
Since you don't believe me,

27:06.650 --> 27:08.650
let me tell you

27:09.150 --> 27:11.730
what is important in my heart.

27:59.880 --> 28:00.910
Why did you...

28:00.960 --> 28:02.390
You want to know

28:02.920 --> 28:05.900
why I can summon your Purple Moon

28:05.930 --> 28:07.460
and even control it?

28:08.120 --> 28:09.550
Because I knew

28:09.550 --> 28:11.290
your power originated from Purple Moon.

28:11.320 --> 28:13.270
The 100 years you've been in Xing Yue Pavilion,

28:13.290 --> 28:14.970
I've been using stellar power

28:15.000 --> 28:17.650
to secretly put up the stellar formation in your body.

28:17.760 --> 28:20.880
So much so I can fully control the source of your divine power.

28:21.120 --> 28:22.210
That's impossible.

28:23.370 --> 28:25.060
Why didn't I notice it?

28:25.090 --> 28:27.170
Of course you didn't.

28:27.490 --> 28:30.160
You cultivate the Soul Lotus with your divine blood every day

28:30.180 --> 28:31.680
and thus your divine soul is unstable.

28:31.810 --> 28:32.810
While it's not easy

28:32.830 --> 28:34.330
to hide it from you

28:34.430 --> 28:35.790
and control your weakness,

28:36.130 --> 28:37.600
it's not difficult either.

28:38.070 --> 28:39.180
You know...

28:40.660 --> 28:42.930
You know what I do every day?

28:43.870 --> 28:45.530
You took advantage of the time I–

28:45.550 --> 28:47.440
It doesn’t matter.

28:47.850 --> 28:49.490
As long as I can

28:49.510 --> 28:51.530
achieve my goal.

29:00.500 --> 29:01.630
Very well...

29:02.670 --> 29:03.820
Good.

29:05.070 --> 29:06.230
Good...

29:10.910 --> 29:11.930
Xing Yue.

29:12.810 --> 29:15.390
Even if you kept me in Xing Yue Pavilion for 100 years

29:15.850 --> 29:18.350
just to control the source of my divine primal power...

29:18.840 --> 29:20.720
Even if you did all this

29:21.060 --> 29:23.370
just for the so-called peace of the Divine Region...

29:27.650 --> 29:29.790
What about our companionship over these 100 years?

29:33.600 --> 29:36.100
We've been together for 100 years.

29:37.830 --> 29:40.110
What am I to you?

29:41.400 --> 29:42.790
In these 100 years...

29:44.460 --> 29:46.130
Have you ever...

29:47.160 --> 29:48.490
truly cared for me?

30:17.560 --> 30:18.600
No.

30:18.930 --> 30:20.150
Never.

30:24.930 --> 30:27.900
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

30:28.360 --> 30:31.210
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

30:32.010 --> 30:35.000
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

30:34.530 --> 30:36.580
These 100 years of companionship

30:35.580 --> 30:37.890
♫This moment feels like forever♫

30:38.540 --> 30:40.290
is but

30:38.710 --> 30:41.470
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

30:41.820 --> 30:43.390
meaningless to me.

30:41.950 --> 30:45.280
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

30:45.750 --> 30:47.310
♫Even if I'll perish♫

30:47.660 --> 30:50.270
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

30:50.760 --> 30:53.430
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

30:54.140 --> 31:02.320
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

30:56.780 --> 30:58.040
So...

30:59.520 --> 31:01.180
it's meaningless...

31:08.980 --> 31:11.770
I don't intend to start a fight between the Three Races.

31:11.790 --> 31:13.400
Purple Moon will return to its owner.

31:13.940 --> 31:15.920
You just need to remember

31:16.040 --> 31:17.950
as long as you don't start a war

31:18.450 --> 31:20.700
and help me protect the peace of the Divine Region,

31:21.840 --> 31:24.360
I will never activate

31:25.940 --> 31:28.040
Purple Moon's stellar restriction.

31:29.940 --> 31:32.910
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

31:33.360 --> 31:36.290
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

31:36.830 --> 31:40.050
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

31:40.590 --> 31:43.230
♫This moment feels like forever♫

31:43.450 --> 31:46.020
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

31:46.650 --> 31:50.300
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

31:50.690 --> 31:52.840
♫Even if I'll perish♫

31:52.970 --> 31:55.530
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

31:55.960 --> 31:59.020
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

31:59.440 --> 32:08.160
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

32:09.530 --> 32:10.610
Divine Lord.

32:38.170 --> 32:40.100
I fell in love,

32:40.130 --> 32:41.820
ignoring your punishment.

32:42.370 --> 32:44.230
Please punish me by sealing off my Contemplations!

32:52.390 --> 32:53.320
Divine Lord!

32:53.340 --> 32:54.500
Stop it!

32:54.530 --> 32:56.440
You received divine punishment in Demon Lord's place.

32:56.460 --> 32:58.220
If you use the power of the Divine Bow to seal your Contemplations now,

32:58.250 --> 32:59.700
you will die!

33:13.420 --> 33:15.010
Divine Lord!

33:20.020 --> 33:22.780
I underestimated my love for him.

33:20.190 --> 33:26.620
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

33:24.340 --> 33:25.560
Xiu Yan...

33:26.350 --> 33:27.550
From tomorrow on,

33:27.420 --> 33:33.340
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

33:28.150 --> 33:29.720
Xing Yue Pavilion will be sealed off.

33:30.750 --> 33:33.070
No one from the Lunar Race is allowed here.

33:33.620 --> 33:35.310
You will be my guardian

33:34.820 --> 33:37.560
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

33:35.930 --> 33:38.920
until my Contemplations were completely sealed off.

33:38.510 --> 33:41.920
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

33:39.040 --> 33:40.520
But your body...

33:41.500 --> 33:43.130
I'm fine.

33:42.400 --> 33:48.760
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

33:44.870 --> 33:47.620
Why didn't you tell Demon Lord the truth?

33:47.820 --> 33:49.870
Why must you bear it all by yourself?

33:49.470 --> 33:56.290
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

33:52.180 --> 33:53.480
He doesn't know

33:53.500 --> 33:54.810
what you did for him.

33:55.370 --> 33:56.930
He doesn't even know he had died once

33:56.950 --> 33:58.640
under the divine punishment of

33:57.090 --> 34:03.270
♫All the answers are already explained♫

33:58.660 --> 33:59.620
the Xing Yue Divine Bow.

34:00.570 --> 34:02.730
You suffered everything for him,

34:03.760 --> 34:06.570
but he only has hate for you.

34:04.360 --> 34:07.040
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

34:07.160 --> 34:08.690
Is it worth it?

34:07.760 --> 34:10.810
♫But we're destined to part♫

34:11.500 --> 34:17.620
♫How can I downplay this?♫

34:12.210 --> 34:14.150
The world is not this simple.

34:15.440 --> 34:18.070
It can't be measured that way.

34:18.469 --> 34:21.489
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

34:19.130 --> 34:20.370
He's not wrong.

34:21.820 --> 34:23.590
It's my fault that

34:22.010 --> 34:24.989
♫When my star falls only for you♫

34:25.110 --> 34:26.409
Heaven doesn't accept him.

34:25.940 --> 34:27.300
♫When the heavens fall♫

34:27.790 --> 34:32.860
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

34:31.690 --> 34:32.480
Divine Lord.

34:33.540 --> 34:36.120
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

34:36.800 --> 34:40.830
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

34:41.719 --> 34:49.900
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

34:49.750 --> 34:51.110
Xing Yue.

34:51.940 --> 34:54.860
I will remember

34:54.909 --> 34:56.679
what you said today.

34:56.960 --> 34:58.450
When I get out of here,

34:58.910 --> 35:01.040
I'll get back at you

35:01.960 --> 35:04.400
for all the humiliation you've put me through today.

35:17.190 --> 35:18.150
Mo Li!

35:18.180 --> 35:19.360
You cultivated with evil magic

35:19.360 --> 35:20.380
and harmed the people.

35:20.410 --> 35:21.490
When the Divine Region finds out,

35:21.510 --> 35:23.090
they will punish you!

35:24.280 --> 35:25.980
No one will know about this

35:26.010 --> 35:27.340
before I succeed.

35:27.930 --> 35:29.410
Because those who know

35:30.700 --> 35:32.260
will die.

36:32.780 --> 36:33.490
Divine Lord.

36:33.520 --> 36:34.650
Demon Lord challenged Night Lord

36:34.670 --> 36:36.230
and was seriously injured in Lunar Hidden Sea.

36:36.260 --> 36:37.810
It has spread throughout the Divine Region.

36:37.830 --> 36:39.950
Got it. Take your leave.

36:40.140 --> 36:40.970
Yes.

36:49.230 --> 36:50.670
Jing Yuan...

36:50.690 --> 36:53.340
Even I can't win her heart.

36:53.430 --> 36:54.870
Do you think the Xing Yue will fall in love with you

36:54.890 --> 36:56.860
just by being with her for a hundred years?

37:00.550 --> 37:02.890
How can you do

37:03.520 --> 37:05.800
what I can't do?

37:14.550 --> 37:15.910
Where have you been?

37:15.930 --> 37:17.400
Took you long enough to come back.

37:25.600 --> 37:27.800
The stellar power hasn't subsided yet.

37:30.350 --> 37:31.530
It's not enough.

37:31.970 --> 37:33.080
I need to absorb

37:33.110 --> 37:35.510
more Lunar and demon divine souls.

37:43.180 --> 37:45.840
The Lunar Race has been in charge of the world for thousands of years.

37:46.520 --> 37:49.050
It's time for a  change.

38:07.860 --> 38:10.540
Hidden power can destroy everything?

38:11.860 --> 38:14.640
People only know that the Three Races of the Divine Region have different powers

38:14.660 --> 38:16.050
and are incompatible.

38:16.080 --> 38:17.730
But no one ever thought that

38:18.180 --> 38:21.230
by combining the divine souls and. power of Three Races

38:21.260 --> 38:24.000
can produce the power to destroy everything.

38:24.800 --> 38:26.470
And this evil magic

38:26.780 --> 38:28.620
was seen by Mo Li.

38:28.660 --> 38:30.570
He used evil magic to strengthen his Hidden Power

38:30.600 --> 38:32.520
and sowed the seeds of destruction.

38:34.000 --> 38:35.150
What about Xing Yue?

38:35.150 --> 38:36.440
Can't she stop it?

38:37.400 --> 38:39.230
Didn't she use the power of the Xing Yue Divine Bow

38:39.230 --> 38:40.670
to seal off the Love Contemplation again?

38:40.770 --> 38:42.960
Love Contemplation is not a static thing.

38:42.980 --> 38:46.110
Sometimes people can't control themselves either.

38:46.880 --> 38:50.130
The Divine Lord has been trying to remove her love for Jing Yuan.

38:50.180 --> 38:52.800
But her love for Jing Yuan is way too deep;

38:53.360 --> 38:55.400
just like spring grass in the wilderness,

38:55.420 --> 38:56.980
it's infinite

38:57.010 --> 38:58.450
and indestructible.

38:58.950 --> 39:00.910
She didn't expect that

39:01.490 --> 39:04.030
even the strongest power in the world

39:04.540 --> 39:06.670
can't stop her feelings.

39:06.970 --> 39:09.100
The love between Xing Yue and Jing Yuan

39:09.130 --> 39:10.850
is so deep.

39:10.870 --> 39:11.670
Since Divine Lord was

39:11.670 --> 39:14.400
unable to seal her Contemplations,

39:15.030 --> 39:17.110
her divine power began to deteriorate.

39:17.470 --> 39:19.840
She was originally transformed by the power of heaven and earth.

39:20.150 --> 39:21.620
The decline of her divine power

39:22.450 --> 39:23.670
means

39:24.580 --> 39:25.790
deities will fall.

39:28.620 --> 39:31.360
But the only person who can help her

39:31.960 --> 39:33.870
became the person who hates her the most.

39:34.410 --> 39:35.960
What did Jing Yuan do?

39:36.200 --> 39:37.870
Jing Yuan entered the Demon Race's secret realm

39:37.890 --> 39:39.220
and cultivated in seclusion.

39:39.780 --> 39:42.580
The Demon Race's secret realm contains strong spiritual energy.

39:42.600 --> 39:44.730
It can help cultivate demonic power quickly.

39:44.950 --> 39:47.730
But 100,000 fierce beasts are also trapped in there.

39:48.160 --> 39:49.800
Those who enter the secret realm

39:50.100 --> 39:51.740
can never survive.

39:52.090 --> 39:55.210
But in order to remove the stellar power within the Purple Moon,

39:55.260 --> 39:58.190
Jing Yuan has been in the secret realm for three years.

39:59.070 --> 40:00.550
In those three years,

40:01.230 --> 40:03.630
due to the decline of divine power,

40:03.660 --> 40:06.310
Divine Lord was sleeping most of the time.

40:07.110 --> 40:08.340
The existence of a Divine Lord

40:08.370 --> 40:10.660
is the foundation of peace in the Divine Region.

40:11.170 --> 40:14.130
She can't let anyone know about this.

40:16.750 --> 40:18.300
Unexpectedly,

40:18.650 --> 40:20.360
after Jing Yuan left the secret realm,

40:20.910 --> 40:23.520
he started the Divine War with the Lunar Race.

40:23.550 --> 40:25.110
The Lunar Race was defeated

40:25.130 --> 40:26.900
and Elder Chang Qing was captured.

40:27.030 --> 40:29.280
Those of the Lunar Race didn't know about Divine Lord's situation

40:29.810 --> 40:31.620
and asked for her

40:31.830 --> 40:34.080
to save Chang Qing.

40:38.430 --> 40:40.510
Divine Lord, you can't go to the Demon Race.

40:40.700 --> 40:42.660
How long did I sleep this time?

40:42.690 --> 40:43.650
10 days.

40:43.900 --> 40:44.860
Divine Lord,

40:44.880 --> 40:46.070
I'll go to the Demon Race in your stead

40:46.090 --> 40:47.600
to save Elder Chang Qing.

40:49.140 --> 40:50.820
I can feel that

40:50.850 --> 40:53.640
he has erased my seal on the Purple Moon.

40:54.260 --> 40:55.570
It's useless for you to go.

40:55.710 --> 40:57.820
But now Demon Lord hate you so much.

40:58.230 --> 40:59.310
In your current condition,

40:59.330 --> 41:00.720
you will definitely lose

41:00.740 --> 41:02.000
in a fight with him.

41:02.190 --> 41:03.710
It's just win or lose.

41:04.400 --> 41:06.660
He just wants to get back at me.

41:06.820 --> 41:08.620
I owe him.

41:08.650 --> 41:09.450
Divine Lord,

41:09.600 --> 41:11.470
if you are trapped there

41:11.490 --> 41:13.780
and can't return to Xing Yue Platform to seal your Contemplation,

41:13.810 --> 41:15.690
your divine power will disappear faster.

41:15.710 --> 41:16.870
I know.

41:22.410 --> 41:24.450
I knew you would come.

41:25.450 --> 41:27.240
But I didn't expect it to be so soon.

41:28.020 --> 41:30.900
It seems that not everyone is insignificant

41:31.290 --> 41:32.930
in your eyes.

41:35.230 --> 41:36.480
Where is Chang Qing?

41:36.930 --> 41:40.100
Since I promised to exchange his life for you to come,

41:40.130 --> 41:41.610
he is still alive.

41:44.050 --> 41:45.250
In that case,

41:46.200 --> 41:47.160
Demon Lord,

41:47.580 --> 41:48.750
let's fight.

41:56.370 --> 41:58.220
You're not using the Xing Yue Bow

41:58.240 --> 41:59.870
to fight with me?

41:59.900 --> 42:01.760
Are you overestimating yourself

42:01.940 --> 42:03.930
or are you despising me?

42:04.550 --> 42:06.150
I have an old agreement

42:06.180 --> 42:07.590
with you.

42:07.810 --> 42:09.030
If we were to fight,

42:09.330 --> 42:10.550
it will be fair.

42:11.050 --> 42:11.930
An old agreement?

42:22.450 --> 42:24.820
If you said this three years ago,

42:25.610 --> 42:27.770
I might think it's because

42:27.790 --> 42:29.630
you love me deeply

42:29.660 --> 42:31.140
and you're pitying me out of that.

42:31.690 --> 42:33.970
Therefore, you couldn't bear to hurt me.

42:41.560 --> 42:43.210
But I've seen

42:43.340 --> 42:46.060
your true colors three years ago.

42:46.090 --> 42:48.250
It's really memorable.

42:49.200 --> 42:51.200
I dare not forget it for even a day.

42:54.780 --> 42:56.620
Since you still remember,

42:56.640 --> 42:58.800
there's no need to waste time to reminisce the past.

42:58.830 --> 43:00.230
I have a lot to do.

43:00.250 --> 43:01.920
I have no time to waste here.

43:03.300 --> 43:04.300
Jing Yuan.

43:04.910 --> 43:06.140
Where is Chang Qing?

43:08.730 --> 43:10.490
Why so anxious?

43:10.560 --> 43:12.780
I put so much effort in asking you here.

43:13.810 --> 43:16.160
Of course there's a big gift I have for you.

43:37.360 --> 43:38.890
Why does this look like...

43:39.350 --> 43:40.470
Xing Yue Pavilion?

43:40.490 --> 43:41.960
With Purple Moon in the sky,

43:41.990 --> 43:43.810
this is still my demonic realm.

43:43.920 --> 43:44.880
This is

43:44.880 --> 43:46.410
I made it after  Xing Yue Pavilion.

43:46.430 --> 43:47.680
Do you like it?

43:50.720 --> 43:51.910
Jing Yuan.

43:51.930 --> 43:53.710
What are you trying to do?

43:53.740 --> 43:55.840
I want you to tell the Divine Region that

43:56.120 --> 43:58.520
the Supreme Deity Xing Yue will be marrying into the Demon Race.

43:58.540 --> 43:59.850
In 10 days,

43:59.880 --> 44:01.420
you'll be marrying me.
